<PB ID="vii" N="vii">
<DIV TYPE="dedication">
<HEAD>TO JOHN BLAND</HEAD>
<L>My Lamb, you are so very small,</L>
<L>You have not learned to read at all;</L>
<L>Yet never a printed book withstands</L>
<L>The urgence of your dimpled hands.</L>
<L>So, though this book is for yourself,</L>
<L>Let mother keep it on the shelf</L>
<L>Till you can read. O days that pass,</L>
<L>That day will come too soon, alas!</L>
</DIV>
